            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Set aside a few<strong> basil </strong>and <strong>mint leaves</strong> and <strong>half </strong>of your<strong> grated Italian hard cheese </strong>for garnish (you'll use the rest later!)</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
