      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>peeled garlic</strong>,<strong> pistachio nuts</strong>, the <strong>remaining grated Italian hard cheese</strong>, <strong>remaining basil </strong>(including the stalks), and<strong> remaining mint leaves </strong>to a <strong>food processor</strong></p><p>Add the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lemon[s]</strong>, 2 1/2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 1/4 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 1/4 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and<strong> pepper</strong></p>",
