      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pot to a medium heat and add the<strong> drained tomato & mozzarella tortelloni</strong> <strong>and peas</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>pistachio pesto</strong> and stir gently until the pasta is coated in the pesto and everything is warmed through – this is your <strong>pistachio pesto with tomato & mozzarella tortelloni</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of starchy pasta water if your sauce is looking a little dry</p><p>Cut the<strong> remaining lemon </strong>into 1 wedge per person</p>",
